Description:
    Copies view partials to your views directory so you can customize comments look and feel

Example:
    ./script/generate comments go --c

    This will create:
        app/views/_comment.haml

    ./script/generate comments go --cs

    This will create:
        app/views/_comments.haml

    ./script/generate comments go --ca

    This will create:
        app/views/_comment_add_form.haml
